experiments/**/kaggle/**/*.pkl
!experiments/**/kaggle/README.md
experiments/**/logs/
experiments/**/checkpoints/
data/balancing_v3_fixed300k_outputs/
data/Federated-Learning-Based-Intrusion-Detection-System-main/data/
data/UNSW_NB15-dataset.zip

# --- Microservices P1 data policy ---
